fields.name: English Ability
fields.description: Level of proficiency at the English language.

fields.name: Year of Entry to United States
fields.description: For immigrants: the year they came to the United States.

fields.name: Has a Sensory Disability
fields.description: A boolean value indicating whether the person has a sensory disability, such as blindness, deafness, etc.

fields.name: Has a Physical Disability
fields.description: A boolean value indicating whether the person has a condition that substantially limits one or more basic physical activities such as walking, climbing stairs, reaching, lifting, or carrying.

fields.name: Has a Mental Disability
fields.description: A boolean value indicating whether the person has a physical, mental, or emotional condition lasting 6 months or more, the person has difficulty learning, remembering or concentrating.

fields.name: Has a Self-care Disability
fields.description: A boolean value indicating whether the person has a physical, mental, or emotional condition lasting 6 months or more, the person has difficulty dressing, bathing, or getting around inside the home.

fields.name: Has a Go-outside-home Disability
fields.description: A boolean value indicating whether the person has a physical, mental, or emotional condition lasting 6 months or more, the person has difficulty going outside the home alone to shop or visit a doctor's office.

fields.name: Has an Employment Disability
fields.description: A boolean value specifying whether the person as a physical, mental, or emotional condition lasting 6 months or more, the person has difficulty working at a job or business.

fields.name: Is Disabled
fields.description: A boolean value indicating if the person is disabled.

fields.name: Has Grandchildren under 18 years
fields.description: A boolean value indicating whether the person has grandchildren that are less than 18 years old

fields.name: Is Responsible for Grandchildren
fields.description: A boolean value indicating whether the person has grandchildren that are younger than 18 years AND is resposible for this grandchild/ these grandchildren.

fields.name: Employment Status
fields.description:
The possible values for this field are:  "Employed","Not in labor force" and "Unemployed".
"Not in labor force" refers to people for whom employment is not an option, because e.g. they are pensioners, are in education, have a long-term disability, are caring for a family member etc.

fields.name: Means of Transportation to Work
fields.description: The means of transportation the person usually uses to get to and from work. Possible options are : "Bicycle","Bus","Car, truck, or van","Ferryboat","Motorcycle","Other","Taxi","Walking"

fields.name: Travel Time to Work (min)
fields.description: The time it takes for this person to travel to work - measured in minutes.

fields.name: works in Industry
fields.description: The industry the person works in.

fields.name: Weeks Worked in the last year
fields.description: The number of weeks of the previous year the person was working at.

fields.name: Hours Worked per Week
fields.description: The average number of hours per week spent working.

fields.name: Self-Employment Income
fields.description: The yearly income coming from self-employment/ entrepreneurial activities.

fields.name: Wage/Salary Income
fields.description: The part of the persons yearly income that was earned as a salary/wage.

fields.name: Social Security Income
fields.description:
The part of the persons yearly income that comes from social benefits.
In America this is e.g.the sum of social security, supplemental security and public assistance income.

fields.name: Retirement Income
fields.description: The part of the person's yearly income which comes from public and private pension.

fields.name: Place of residence (US State)
fields.description: For people living in the United States of America: the State they live in.

fields.name: Time Leaving for Work
fields.description: The usual time the person get's out of the house to go to work.

fields.name: Occupation
fields.description:
The occupation/profession of the person. 
The categories used here are from the 'Census 2000 Occupational Classification' - see page 51 of this document: https://www.census.gov/content/dam/Census/library/working-papers/2003/demo/techpaper2000.pdf

fields.name: Income ($/year)
fields.description:
The total yearly income of the person - measured in Dollars. 
This is the sum of Self-Employment Income, Wages/Salary, Social Security and Retirement Income.

fields.name: Preferred Political Candidate
fields.description: The political candidate for whom the will vote in the next election.
